68fd118b-4393-42d2-a2c6-ddc64b23254c	debit_card_specializing		Gas station in the Czech Republic implies that Country = 'CZE'	\N
e3de249c-e4fc-4700-b58c-11d24110b79a	debit_card_specializing		Czech Republic can be represented as the Country value in the gasstations table is 'CZE'	\N
fbdef091-9576-47dc-a4d7-aab54a5e3506	debit_card_specializing		'2012/8/25' can be represented by '2012-08-25'	\N
de40b188-42e8-469e-a3ba-2ac4ed2f4d9c	debit_card_specializing		'2012/8/24' can be represented by '2012-08-24'; 	\N
1b187079-fdb0-4ac9-9098-ec38edc93790	debit_card_specializing		'2012/8/23' can be represented by '2012-08-23'	\N
410c6386-c4d1-474d-ad2e-23c3d5a159b4	debit_card_specializing		'2012/8/26' can be represented by '2012-08-26'; The morning refers to the time before '13:00:00'	\N
307d9cce-e743-4cf8-800f-a9148e9f9af4	debit_card_specializing		'2012/8/24 12:42:00' can refer to date = '2012-08-24' AND T1.time = '12:42:00' in the database	\N
65647809-8c5e-42e5-890a-408a66598e98	debit_card_specializing		'2012/8/23 21:20:00' can refer to date = '2012-08-23' AND T1.time = '21:20:00' in the database	\N
98358b07-60bf-44a8-a633-e4809f1a41eb	debit_card_specializing		'2012/8/24' can be represented by '2012-08-24'; expense and the consumption has the similar meaning.	\N
ed70a37d-96d7-44d1-831c-95e9f8880eb9	debit_card_specializing		Czech Republic can be represented as the Country value in the gasstations table is 'CZE'; '2012/8/26' can be represented by '2012-08-26'; during 8:00-9:00 can be represented as Time BETWEEN '08:00:00' AND '09:00:00'	\N
9b10f545-d8d3-4e28-9702-25d4ca6233f2	debit_card_specializing		June of 2013 means Date contains '201306' in the yearmonth.date of the database	\N
537e282f-a647-4ac1-b693-07ec8c1bd686	debit_card_specializing		'2012/8/24' can be represented by '2012-08-24'	\N
cac6bcec-c0b6-46e9-9bbb-7853e08b33be	debit_card_specializing		'2012/8/24' can be represented by '2012-08-24'; Consumption decrease rate = (consumption_2012 - consumption_2013) / consumption_2012	\N
26a9fc51-0272-4686-97c4-6f338e2da78c	debit_card_specializing		January 2012 refers to the Date value = '201201'	\N
4b4c89b7-79ee-4c1b-9d7e-da6a4d911978	debit_card_specializing		Description of products contains full name	\N
0dbee644-36aa-4282-8db5-d14ff113acee	debit_card_specializing		average price per single item = Total(price) / Total(amount)	\N
b030a277-6b0e-4d35-b35f-862e0a2a2346	debit_card_specializing		August of 2012 refers to the Date value = '201208' ; Price per unit of product = Price / Amount;	\N
