07bd377b-c98f-4503-8153-bb9f896dcf55	toxicology	What type of label is not on molecules with atoms with tin?	SELECT DISTINCT T2.label FROM atom AS T1 INNER JOIN molecule AS T2 ON T1.molecule_id = T2.molecule_id WHERE T1.element != 'sn'
