a3cb3467-ce5d-4f3d-9dbe-5052ebe0aab9	toxicology	What are the bond IDs that have the same atom ID 2 of TR000_2?	SELECT T.bond_id FROM connected AS T WHERE T.atom_id2 = 'TR000_2'
089eb9bd-8846-45d3-9656-050455dce0fc	toxicology	Please list top five molecules that have double bonds in alphabetical order.	SELECT DISTINCT T.molecule_id FROM bond AS T WHERE T.bond_type = '=' ORDER BY T.molecule_id LIMIT 5
