8a7411d1-9b7f-4346-ae0f-fdf85306192f	european_football_2	What is the ADO Den Haag team freedom of movement in the 1st two thirds of the pitch?	SELECT DISTINCT t2.buildUpPlayPositioningClass FROM Team AS t1 INNER JOIN Team_attributes AS t2 ON t1.team_fifa_api_id = t2.team_fifa_api_id WHERE t1.team_long_name = 'ADO Den Haag'
