e6d9cfda-dd24-4fc9-be0f-16af9ef0a72e	european_football_2	What is the average number of goals made by Parma as the away team while playing in Italy?	SELECT CAST(SUM(T1.away_team_goal) AS REAL) / COUNT(T1.id) FROM "Match" AS T1 INNER JOIN TEAM AS T2 ON T1.away_team_api_id = T2.team_api_id INNER JOIN Country AS T3 ON T1.country_id = T3.id WHERE T2.team_long_name = 'Parma' AND T3.name = 'Italy'
