67f3a086-c942-42f8-bb47-d1b2a39c8654	european_football_2	Please provide top five football players' IDs who are among the lowest potential players and prefer to use the right foot when attacking.	SELECT id FROM Player_Attributes WHERE preferred_foot = 'right' ORDER BY potential DESC LIMIT 5
