0a9a37d9-5d88-4c2d-8e21-5d53096ed21f	european_football_2	What was the final score for the match on September 24, 2008, in the Belgian Jupiler League between the home team and the away team?	SELECT t2.home_team_goal, t2.away_team_goal FROM League AS t1 INNER JOIN Match AS t2 ON t1.id = t2.league_id WHERE t1.name = 'Belgium Jupiler League' AND t2.`date` LIKE '2008-09-24%'
