3e439cf9-3e52-48bf-8c22-af539caf8565	thrombosis_prediction	Are there more in-patient or outpatient who were male? What is the deviation in percentage?	SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN Admission = '+' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / SUM(CASE WHEN Admission = '-' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) FROM Patient WHERE SEX = 'M'
d6746f2b-2e4a-49a1-8ed3-581c3424e8a2	thrombosis_prediction	What is the percentage of female patient were born after 1930?	SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', Birthday) > '1930' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(*) FROM Patient WHERE SEX = 'F'
